## highlightjs-line-numbers.js

[highlightjs](https://highlightjs.readthedocs.io/en/latest/line-numbers.html) the only way to show that they are better is to set up some usability research on the subject. I doubt anyone would bother to do it bother to do it.

[highlightjs-line-numbers.js](https://github.com/wcoder/highlightjs-line-numbers.js/)  plugin

highlightjs-line-numbers.js  Bower/Npm CDN

## highlight.js

 highlight.js 

volantis `~\themes\volantis\layout_plugins\highlight\`  `script.ejs` 

```
<% if (theme.plugins.highlightjs.js) { %>
<%- js(theme.plugins.highlightjs.js) %>
<script src="//cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/highlightjs-line-numbers.js@2.8.0/dist/highlightjs-line-numbers.min.js"></script>
<script>hljs.initHighlightingOnLoad();</script>
<script>hljs.initLineNumbersOnLoad({singleLine:true});</script>
<script>
<% } %>
volantis.pjax.push(()=>{
    document.querySelectorAll('pre code').forEach((block) => {
    hljs.highlightBlock(block);
    hljs.lineNumbersBlock(block,{singleLine:true});
    });
},"highlightjs")
</script> 
```

