/* for block of numbers */
.hljs-ln-numbers {
    -webkit-touch-callout: none;
    -webkit-user-select: none;
    -khtml-user-select: none;
    -moz-user-select: none;
    -ms-user-select: none;
    user-select: none;

    text-align: center;
    color: #ccc;
    border-right: 1px solid #CCC;
    vertical-align: top;
    padding-right: 5px;

    /* your custom style here */
}

/* for block of code */
.hljs-ln-code {
    padding-left: 10px;
}
```

  `~/themes/volantis/source/css/`  `style.styl` 

```
@import '_other/*'
```

##  _config.yml  _config.volantis.yml

  `_config.yml`   disable `highlight`  enable `highlightjs`

```
# 
highlight:
  enable: false
  hljs: true
```

  `_config.volantis.yml`  #

```
highlightjs:
    copy_code: true
    # 2#
    js: ...
    css: ....
```

 `_config.volantis.yml` 

```
  light:
    # ()
    block: '#f6f6f6'     
    # ()
    codeblock: '#FFF7EA'
    # 
    inlinecode:  '#4282d7'      # '#c74f00'
```

